results.name: Permutation of natural numbers induced by Catalan Automorphism *A089861 acting on the binary trees/parenthesizations encoded by A014486/A063171.
comment: This automorphism effects the following transformation on the unlabeled rooted plane binary trees (letters A, B, C refer to arbitrary subtrees located on those nodes and () stands for an implied terminal node).
See the Karttunen OEIS-Wiki link for a detailed explanation of how to obtain a given integer sequence from this definition.
link: A. Karttunen, C-program for computing this sequence
Index entries for signature-permutations induced by Catalan automorphisms
program: (Scheme functions implementing this automorphism on list-structures/S-expressions, both constructive (*A089861) and destructive (*A089861!) versions:)
(define (*A089861 s) (cond ((not (pair? s)) s) ((not (pair? (car s))) (cons (cdr s) (car s))) (else (cons (cdar s) (cons (caar s) (cdr s))))))
(define (*A089861! s) (cond ((pair? s) (cond ((pair? (car s)) (swap! (car s)) (robr! s)) (else (swap! s))))) s)
(define (swap! s) (let ((ex-car (car s))) (set-car! s (cdr s)) (set-cdr! s ex-car) s))
(define (robr! s) (let ((ex-cdr (cdr s))) (set-cdr! s (caar s)) (set-car! (car s) ex-cdr) (swap! (car s)) (swap! s) s))
